<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I guess I just don't understand the use of such a spell.  I'm more a person for results, rather than "oooh looky here, I've got a toy".<P>The illusion sounds like fun, nothing else.  First off, in large battles you're AoEd then thwapped dead in three shots.  so will your little doppleganger.  The second it gets hit with an AoE mez or AoE damage, the illusion is gone.  In small battles, people will say "wow, that goborchend just turned into a sorceress.  And it's sort of standing there while the other one is casting a bunch of damaging spells. decisions decisions."<P>It seems like a lot of coding.  I'd rather have them spend coding time fixing the problems that are already there, rather than adding something new. :-(  I just want to be a mez queen like I once was!
</FONT>
